<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>My Website - With Logo</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 50px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4; /* Light background for contrast */
            color: #333;
        }
        .header {
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        .logo {
            max-width: 180px; /* Adjust size as you like */
            height: auto;
            display: block; /* Ensures the image takes its own line */
            margin: 0 auto 20px auto; /* Centers the logo and adds bottom margin */
        }
        h1 {
            color: #222;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 50px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #eee;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <!-- This is where your logo will go -->
        <img src="path/to/your/new_logo_with_star.png" alt="Crescent Moon, Star, and Kaaba Logo" class="logo">
        <h1>Welcome to Our Spiritual Journey</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p>We are delighted to have you join us. Explore our services and learn more about our community.</p>
        <p>This page features our unique logo, symbolizing guidance and faith, incorporated beautifully into the design.</p>
        <p>Feel free to browse around and discover what we have to offer.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2026 Your Website Name. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
